      "rationale": "NIH predictions compared against in-vitro bovine blood measurements at all 5 operating points. Maximum absolute error 14.7%, mean 8.3%. Validation metric computed per ASME V&V 20. Gradation 2 requirement met. Note: comparison conflates Newtonian model error with experimental scatter; non-Newtonian contribution not isolated."
